{"id":9031,"date":"2020-07-24T08:29:30","date_gmt":"2020-07-24T08:29:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=9031"},"modified":"2021-08-17T02:33:35","modified_gmt":"2021-08-17T02:33:35","slug":"vat-lieu-noi-that-hien-dai","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/vat-lieu-noi-that-hien-dai\/","title":{"rendered":"NGU\u1ed2N C\u1ea2M H\u1ee8NG TRONG N\u1ed8I TH\u1ea4T HI\u1ec6N \u0110\u1ea0I"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><strong> Trong<a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\"> thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i<\/a>, vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, hay d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf nhu c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng. S\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u nh\u1eb1m g\u1ee3i l\u00ean nh\u1eefng rung c\u1ea3m, c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng gian l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. B\u1edfi, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i hay lo l\u1eafng, \u1ea5m \u00e1p hay \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9c,&#8230;t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1edfi c\u00e1ch l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed t\u1eebng m\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t.  <\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-3-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"vat-lieu-noi-that\" class=\"wp-image-9032\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-3-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-3.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, th\u00f4ng qua ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang t\u00ednh th\u1ea7n phong c\u00e1ch Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i. Ng\u00e0y nay, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n khoa h\u1ecdc c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng phong ph\u00fa, \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i theo nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00f3m kh\u00e1c nhau. Trong n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu theo c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang g\u1ed3m g\u1ed7, kim lo\u1ea1i, k\u00ednh &#8211; g\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u00e1 &#8211; b\u00ea t\u00f4ng,\u2026<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u trong n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u1ea3i qua qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eeb h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd t\u1edbi \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i; c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean kinh nghi\u1ec7m, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c chung ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed7i phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i ri\u00eang m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7. B\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u trong phong c\u00e1ch Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i, ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 Byzan lu\u00f4n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i trong vi\u1ec7c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao nh\u1ea5t trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf.&nbsp;<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/9-1-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"vat-lieu-noi-that-hien-dai\" class=\"wp-image-9033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/9-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/9-1-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/9-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/9-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/9-1-450x253.jpg 450w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/9-1-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/9-1.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>G\u1ed7<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1eeb xa x\u01b0a, g\u1ed7 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 tham gia ch\u00ednh v\u00e0o c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0. Do \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh d\u1ec5 gia c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 mang t\u1edbi c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u1ea5m \u00e1p m\u00e0 g\u1ed7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i trong kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb tr\u1ea7n, s\u00e0n, t\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng,&#8230;Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o s\u1edf th\u00edch, nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7 m\u00e0 b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u g\u1ed7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia c\u00f4ng m\u1ecbn hay gi\u1eef n\u00e9t th\u00f4 r\u00e1p hoang s\u01a1.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"819\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-4-1024x819.jpg\" alt=\"vat-lieu-noi-that\" class=\"wp-image-9034\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-4-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-4-300x240.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-4-768x614.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-4-1536x1229.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-4.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ng\u00e0y nay, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc trong khoa h\u1ecdc c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7. C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i g\u1ed7 MDF, HDF, g\u1ed7 d\u00e1n, veneer \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ec1u mang v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c t\u00ednh cong v\u00eanh, co ng\u00f3t, r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t \u1edf g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n cho s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, lu\u00f4n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng g\u1ed7, b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu l\u00e0m d\u1ee5ng s\u1ebd v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 g\u00e2y n\u00ean c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf, ch\u1eadt h\u1eb9p.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"614\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/logo-pn-1024x614.jpg\" alt=\"vat-lieu-noi-that-hien-dai\" class=\"wp-image-9035\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/logo-pn-1024x614.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/logo-pn-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/logo-pn-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/logo-pn.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>\u0110\u00e1 &#8211; B\u00ea t\u00f4ng<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m chung c\u1ee7a hai d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e1 &#8211; b\u00ea t\u00f4ng l\u00e0 thu\u1ed9c t\u00ednh \u201cv\u0129nh c\u1eedu\u201d. N\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh m\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang mang t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng x\u00fac c\u1ea3m kh\u00e1c nhau.&nbsp;<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"819\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4-2-1024x819.jpg\" alt=\"vat-lieu-noi-that-hien-dai\" class=\"wp-image-9036\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4-2-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4-2-300x240.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4-2-768x614.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4-2-1536x1229.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4-2.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Hi\u1ec7n nay, \u0111\u00e1 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u \u1ed1p l\u00e1t \u1edf d\u1ea1ng t\u1ea5m m\u1ecfng nh\u01b0 \u1ed1p t\u01b0\u1eddng tivi, t\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ebfp, m\u1eb7t b\u1ebfp,&#8230;V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean qua v\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 Viscotone, Marble lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 mang t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng cho kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1c, v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e1 mang t\u00ednh \u201cl\u1ea1nh\u201d n\u00ean khi \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng trong n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u1edf nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ri\u00eang nh\u01b0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, m\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian sinh ho\u1ea1t chung nh\u01b0 ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, b\u1ebfp, nh\u00e0 t\u1eafm v\u1edbi kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.&nbsp;<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"614\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-4-1024x614.jpg\" alt=\"vat-lieu-noi-that-hien-dai\" class=\"wp-image-9037\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-4-1024x614.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-4-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-4-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-4-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-4.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1, b\u00ea t\u00f4ng l\u00e0 v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn \u1edf c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 XIX. T\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00ea t\u00f4ng m\u1edbi d\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, lo\u1ea1i v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 tr\u1ea7n b\u00ea t\u00f4ng, d\u1ea7m b\u00ea t\u00f4ng trong x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i t\u01b0 duy m\u1edf, s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u trong phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 Byzan \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed3ng gh\u00e9p v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n, ph\u00f3ng kho\u00e1ng m\u00e0 tr\u1ea7n tr\u1ee5i c\u1ee7a d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-5-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"chat-cam-vat-lieu\" class=\"wp-image-9038\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-5-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-5-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-5-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-5-450x253.jpg 450w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-5-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2